<https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/CO-META> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> "Ontology for Combinatory Optimization Metaheuristics"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/CO-META> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> "Ontología para Metaheurísticas de Optimización Combinatoria"@es .
<https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/CO-META> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/source> <https://github.com/ontologies-ULL/CO-META> .
<https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/CO-META> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "Esta ontología proporciona un marco estructurado para la interoperabilidad de fuentes de datos y aplicaciones en el contexto de las metaheurísticas de optimización combinatoria."@es .
<https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/CO-META> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "This ontology provides a structured framework for the interoperability of data sources and applications in the context of combinatory optimization metaheuristics."@en .
